00:27:46.540 --> 00:27:47.541
Yeah. I remember.

513
00:27:47.624 --> 00:27:49.960
He sat in a corner booth.
He had a drink.

514
00:27:50.043 --> 00:27:51.211
But that's all I know.

515
00:27:51.295 --> 00:27:52.963
Where do they keep
surveillance footage?

516
00:27:53.046 --> 00:27:54.840
In the back.

517
00:27:55.507 --> 00:27:57.593
But even I'm not allowed in there.

518
00:28:04.016 --> 00:28:05.017
Thank you.

519
00:28:07.686 --> 00:28:09.855
<i>And there she was again.</i>

520
00:28:09.938 --> 00:28:12.482
<i>I had to admit. she was beautiful.</i>

521
00:28:12.566 --> 00:28:14.693
<i>She had a body
that carried her head around.</i>

522
00:28:14.776 --> 00:28:16.528
<i>and a butt that seemed to say.</i>

523
00:28:16.612 --> 00:28:18.697
<i>"Hello. I'm a talking butt."</i>

524
00:28:19.656 --> 00:28:21.617
<i>Elegant? Yeah. I'd say so.</i>

525
00:28:21.700 --> 00:28:22.868
Oh!

526
00:28:22.951 --> 00:28:25.454
<i>But like a teenager
with three babysitting jobs.</i>

527
00:28:25.537 --> 00:28:27.915
<i>I didn't need another babysitting job.</i>

528
00:28:27.998 --> 00:28:29.583
Hello. Lieutenant.

529
00:28:29.666 --> 00:28:31.210
What the hell are you doing here?

530
00:28:31.293 --> 00:28:32.878
I'm doing the same thing you are.

531
00:28:32.961 --> 00:28:35.214
I told you I wasn't gonna
sit around and wait.

532
00:28:35.297 --> 00:28:37.633
Listen. this isn't
one of your stories.

533
00:28:37.716 --> 00:28:41.595
Average civilian women
