534
00:28:41.678 --> 00:28:42.971
Oh. you read my book.

535
00:28:43.680 --> 00:28:44.681
What'd you think?

536
00:28:45.224 --> 00:28:46.475
I think it's a fantasy.

537
00:28:46.975 --> 00:28:49.228
A woman puts on a wig and sunglasses

538
00:28:49.311 --> 00:28:51.021
and suddenly she's an assassin?

539
00:28:51.104 --> 00:28:52.481
But did you enjoy it?

540
00:28:53.357 --> 00:28:54.816
It had some good parts.

541
00:28:55.859 --> 00:28:56.944
Ah!

542
00:28:57.027 --> 00:28:58.362
Lieutenant Drebin.

543
00:28:58.445 --> 00:29:00.280
Does he know you're Simon's sister?

544
00:29:00.989 --> 00:29:03.325
- No.
- Good. Let's keep it that way.

545
00:29:03.408 --> 00:29:04.826
What a wonderful surprise.

546
00:29:04.910 --> 00:29:06.328
Fine. thank you.

547
00:29:06.411 --> 00:29:08.455
Beautiful place you've got here.

548
00:29:08.538 --> 00:29:10.165
Can't smell the dead animals at all.

549
00:29:10.249 --> 00:29:11.500
Thank you.

550
00:29:12.417 --> 00:29:13.752
Uh. can I get you a drink?

551
00:29:13.835 --> 00:29:15.629
Just water. And sparkling.

552
00:29:19.800 --> 00:29:22.386
And who is this stunning creature?

553
00:29:22.970 --> 00:29:24.429
I don't believe we've met.

554
00:29:24.513 --> 00:29:27.307
- Well. I'm--
- Uh. th... this is Miss...

555
00:29:28.058 --> 00:29:29.393
Cherry...

556
00:29:29.935 --> 00:29:31.103
Roosevelt...

557
00:29:31.895 --> 00:29:34.106
Fat Bozo Chowing Spaghetti.

558
00:29:34.773 --> 00:29:36.566
- What an interesting name.
- Yes.

559
00:29:37.109 --> 00:29:38.110
Thank you.

560
00:29:38.193 --> 00:29:40.362
So. Lieutenant. what brings you here?

561
00:29:40.445 --> 00:29:43.865
I was hoping you could let me
take a look at your security footage.

562
00:29:43.949 --> 00:29:45.659
Oh. May I ask why?

563
00:29:45.742 --> 00:29:47.035
Go right ahead.

564
00:29:51.373 --> 00:29:52.416
Uh...

565
00:29:52.499 --> 00:29:54.626
Unfortunately. I can't
show you security footage.

566
00:29:54.710 --> 00:29:56.878
Our members trust
that we will provide them

567
00:29:56.962 --> 00:29:58.755
with the highest level of privacy.

568
00:29:59.339 --> 00:30:00.757
I hope you understand.

569
00:30:00.841 --> 00:30:01.925
I'm starting to.

570
00:30:03.010 --> 00:30:04.720
Well. thank you so much for the drink.

571
00:30:04.803 --> 00:30:06.930
It's getting late.
We really must be going.

572
00:30:07.014 --> 00:30:08.015
So soon?

573
00:30:08.098 --> 00:30:10.225
I hope you're not leaving.
too. Miss Spaghetti.

574
00:30:10.309 --> 00:30:13.103
- Oh. well. I--
- Yes. she's leaving. too.

575
00:30:13.186 --> 00:30:15.439
Early morning at Disneyland tomorrow.

576
00:30:15.522 --> 00:30:17.065
She's one of those Disney adults.

577
00:30:17.149 --> 00:30:20.652
Obsessed. really.
Her bed is covered in dolls.

578
00:30:20.736 --> 00:30:22.446
Oh. Miss Spaghetti.

579
00:30:22.529 --> 00:30:23.530
please stay for a drink.

580
00:30:24.239 --> 00:30:26.491
Uh. you don't mind. do you. Drebin?

581
00:30:26.575 --> 00:30:27.659
Be my guest.

582
00:30:27.743 --> 00:30:29.328
Wonderful. I'll get a table.

583
