You get the footage.
I'll keep him occupied.

584
00:30:34.249 --> 00:30:36.043
I'm... Absolutely not!

585
00:30:43.717 --> 00:30:44.926
Oh. thank you.

586
00:30:46.470 --> 00:30:48.513
Wow. This place is amazing.

587
00:30:48.597 --> 00:30:50.223
Ah. Thank you.

588
00:30:50.891 --> 00:30:52.976
Miss Spaghetti. may I speak freely?

589
00:30:53.060 --> 00:30:54.269
I'd prefer English.

590
00:30:55.020 --> 00:30:56.480
You're much too sophisticated...

591
00:30:56.563 --> 00:30:58.190
...for the likes of Frank Drebin.

592
00:30:58.273 --> 00:31:00.484
Oh. I'm not with Drebin.

593
00:31:00.567 --> 00:31:02.569
Oh. Well. that's wonderful news!

594
00:31:02.652 --> 00:31:04.154
Oof!

595
