Cheers.

596
00:31:13.205 --> 00:31:14.664
From Bill Cosby's private estate.

597
00:31:14.748 --> 00:31:16.583
Mm.

598
00:31:46.738 --> 00:31:47.739
Gah! Oof!

599
00:31:56.665 --> 00:31:58.917
That hurt!

600
00:31:59.000 --> 00:32:01.711
Shoot!

601
00:32:01.795 --> 00:32:03.922
Mom. Mom. now is not a good time.

602
00:32:04.631 --> 00:32:06.842
Mom. please. I'll call you back.

603
00:32:06.925 --> 00:32:09.511
I got to go. I got to go.
I got to go now.

604
00:32:11.638 --> 00:32:12.973
So. tell me.

605
00:32:13.557 --> 00:32:15.267
what have you been working on lately?

606
00:32:15.350 --> 00:32:18.145
Oh. let's not talk about work.
Let's talk about play.

607
00:32:20.856 --> 00:32:22.732
Uh. do you like jazz. Miss Spaghetti?

608
00:32:22.816 --> 00:32:24.484
- Like it?
- Hm.

609
00:32:24.568 --> 00:32:26.403
- I love it.
- I love it.

610
00:32:29.322 --> 00:32:30.782
Sir. Um...

611
00:32:31.783 --> 00:32:32.909
We've got a problem.

612
00:32:32.993 --> 00:32:34.077
Not now.

613
00:32:34.161 --> 00:32:35.287
- No. it's quite...
- Not now.

614
00:32:36.496 --> 00:32:38.665
Yes. sir.

615
00:32:39.791 --> 00:32:41.710
This one's for my electric new friend.

616
00:32:42.544 --> 00:32:43.879
Richard Cane.

617
00:32:43.962 --> 00:32:45.046
Wow!

618
00:32:45.797 --> 00:32:47.632
<i>Sassafras Chicken</i> in D.

619
