Make it extra lumpy. boys.

620
00:33:04.357 --> 00:33:07.486
<i>I've always said
fighting is a lot like jazz music.</i>

621
00:33:07.569 --> 00:33:08.987
<i>A scat-like improv</i>

622
00:33:09.070 --> 00:33:12.407
