Oh...

625
00:33:29.549 --> 00:33:30.800
I'm fine.

626
00:33:50.862 --> 00:33:52.405
Yeah!

627
00:34:06.211 --> 00:34:09.339
<i>There's two things I love.
My stay-at-home girlfriend</i>

628
00:34:09.422 --> 00:34:10.799
- <i>and Gorilla Nut...</i>
- Come on.

629
00:34:10.882 --> 00:34:13.051
<i>...enhanced drink supplement for men.</i>

630
00:34:13.134 --> 00:34:14.511
<i>Don't follow fad diets
and fake workouts.</i>

631
00:34:14.594 --> 00:34:15.762
<i>You want to get ripped?</i>

632
00:34:15.845 --> 00:34:18.598
