going on here.

647
00:35:33.089 --> 00:35:35.175
You wake up
my husband. I swear to God...

648
00:35:35.258 --> 00:35:36.635
- I'm sorry.
- What the hell

649
00:35:36.718 --> 00:35:38.011
were you thinking. Drebin?

650
00:35:38.094 --> 00:35:40.055
Richard Cane is a very powerful man.

651
00:35:40.138 --> 00:35:42.515
And he makes a lot of hefty
donations to this city.

652
00:35:42.599 --> 00:35:44.476
including the new car you're driving.

653
00:35:44.559 --> 00:35:45.769
Richard Cane is dirty.

654
00:35:45.852 --> 00:35:48.271
