657
00:35:52.609 --> 00:35:54.653
That's it. You're suspended!

658
00:35:54.736 --> 00:35:56.112
Suspended?

659
00:35:56.738 --> 00:35:58.490
What did I say about waking Ronald?

660
00:35:58.573 --> 00:35:59.949
He has a Fitzgerald presentation

661
00:36:00.033 --> 00:36:01.076
tomorrow.

662
00:36:01.159 --> 00:36:06.206
And if Morimoto doesn't
accept his vertical-integration pitch.

663
00:36:06.289 --> 00:36:10.043
Bill Cantor will leapfrog him
for the third year in a row.

664
00:36:10.126 --> 00:36:12.128
- But Ronald trained Bill.
- Exactly!

665
00:36:12.212 --> 00:36:13.755
I've got no choice.

666
00:36:13.838 --> 00:36:15.840
I'm putting you on ice. Two weeks.

667
00:36:15.924 --> 00:36:16.925
Effective immediately.

668
00:36:17.008 --> 00:36:18.301
Now get out.

669
00:36:19.719 --> 00:36:22.013
We're all
rooting for you. Ronald.

670
00:36:22.097 --> 00:36:23.515
Give 'em hell tomorrow.

671
00:36:38.071 --> 00:36:39.114
Rough night?

672
00:36:40.490 --> 00:36:41.783
Oh. It's you.

673
00:36:42.492 --> 00:36:44.953
