674
00:36:45.036 --> 00:36:47.122
Listen. I feel for you. I really do.

675
00:36:47.205 --> 00:36:49.541
But I had to beat up
a lot of henchmen tonight.

676
00:36:49.624 --> 00:36:50.709
Men with daughters!

677
00:36:50.792 --> 00:36:53.420
Oh. come on. You wouldn't even
