694
00:37:37.922 --> 00:37:39.174
Not for a second.

695
00:38:01.321 --> 00:38:02.447
Thank you.

696
00:38:09.496 --> 00:38:11.498
Uh... excuse the mess.

697
00:38:11.956 --> 00:38:12.957
I. uh...

698
00:38:13.625 --> 00:38:15.418
