<i>Lookin' in your eyes</i>

754
00:41:38.705 --> 00:41:40.581
<i>I see a paradise</i>

755
00:41:40.665 --> 00:41:44.836
<i>This world that I found
ls too good to be true</i>

756
00:41:46.129 --> 00:41:48.339
<i>Standin' here beside you</i>

757
