00:42:31.174 --> 00:42:33.801
<i>We'll still have each other</i>

769
00:42:33.885 --> 00:42:36.262
<i>Nothing's gonna stop us</i>

770
00:42:36.345 --> 00:42:38.723
<i>Nothing's gonna stop us now</i>

